oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Livery Stable
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Edwin Best
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Greenback (Tenn.); Business; Montgomery, Cal; Montgomery, Tom;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Two men, one in a four-wheeled buggy pulled by two horses, and one on a horse, outside of the Greenback Livery Stable. Posters advertising brands of tobacco or chew are on the open door and on the exterior wall, which has vertical barn siding.
